| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5509 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonransomware)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 870752b9-41fd-5ec5-a169-04c496f13b6d"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
